  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pay the 28 billion owed to renewable electricity immediately",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has directed the Ceylon Electricity Board to pay the amount of 28 billion rupees due for a period of six months for the acquisition of renewable energy within the next three months.",
        "Those institutions had complained to the Public Utilities Commission regarding the money owed by the Ceylon Electricity Board for the electricity obtained from wind power plants, solar power plants and private power plants under renewable energy.",
        "The commission, which has considered the complaints, has directed that the money be paid within the next three months."
      ],
